title: 028: Our Buddy Craig Capurso
description: Sal, Adam & Justin interview their friend Craig Capurso who is an IFBB Pro physique competitor, Team Bodybuilding.com spokesmodel, Cellucor Athlete and entrepreneur. In this episode Craig and the MindPump crew reveal a secret history that could have forever changed MindPump as you know it today.
